title: Fallon paraded through Harvard as 'Emperor of Comedy'
text: Fallon paraded through Harvard as 'Emperor of Comedy' Sunday, 25 October 2015 (12 minutes ago) Los Angeles, Oct 25 : Comedian and talk show host Jimmy Fallon was at the centre of Harvard Lampoon's annual parade this year, where he got treated as the "Emperor of Comedy" and was paraded in a Roman chariot. The comedian was the seventh recipient of humor magazine Harvard Lampoon's Elmer Award for Excellence in Humor.
